Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.73,0:00:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要身兼先鋒和大將兩職嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.79,0:00:08.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  先鋒一上來就戴著頭盔看不清面貌的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.21,0:00:10.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣  這主意不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.57,0:00:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這樣會露餡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.18,0:00:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體型又不能變化  看動作就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:20.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以先鋒戰要內斂一點去對戰  一半實力就好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.92,0:00:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一半…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.70,0:00:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大將戰要全力以赴  好像另外一個人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.15,0:00:32.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一半…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.03,0:00:35.58,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\fad(300,0)}室江高中·先鋒\N川添珠姬（紅方）\N（先取一分）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.03,0:00:35.58,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,0)}町戶高中·先鋒\N原田小夏（白方）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.26,0:00:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦老師  就算是一半…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.93,0:00:40.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二局！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.35,0:00:45.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠她在部團活動裡就沒有認真過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.73,0:00:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連一半都沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.48,0:00:53.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面——！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.13,0:02:30.06,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}第6話\N川添珠姬與遲到的武禮葉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.63,0:02:32.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽結束！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面有效  獲勝…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:43.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  有認真在工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:48.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉各位  我沒派上什麼用場
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.51,0:02:51.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  別在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.59,0:02:55.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原田學了很久  而且擁有二段資格
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都很認真地練習  也很有進取心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.05,0:03:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們的No.2了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是對手方面有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.05,0:03:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太強了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.63,0:03:12.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添？新生嗎？到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.81,0:03:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:19.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小次郎  先鋒上哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.58,0:03:23.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？啊…她已經回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.51,0:03:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.33,0:03:28.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  那個…好像是和牙醫有約什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:29.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙醫？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠牙齒不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.36,0:03:36.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有告訴她今天是比賽吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.22,0:03:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為前輩你們遲到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.41,0:03:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這對你們也是個很好的刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.71,0:03:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把氣勢給我拿出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺川…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:51.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.24,0:03:58.69,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}室江高中·次鋒  宮崎都（紅方）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:04:01.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}町戶高中·次鋒  淺川明美（白方）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.04,0:03:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次鋒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:58.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅方  宮崎都
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:01.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白方  淺川明美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.02,0:04:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手的樣子好像有點奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:08.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是和男朋友…出什麼事情了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.92,0:04:09.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜中了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.61,0:04:14.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種傢伙…那種傢伙…那種傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.16,0:04:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.97,0:04:16.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上  小都都！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.43,0:04:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻啊攻啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:28.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺川  你這和外行人一樣在搞什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你擅長的步法哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.89,0:04:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出場外  回來！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.97,0:04:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都再大點聲！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你行的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:45.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  老師  我可以去上廁所嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.73,0:04:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:48.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正在比賽啊！給我忍下！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.13,0:04:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  可是我已經忍不住了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少等小都都的比賽結束…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.40,0:05:01.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  段  你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.71,0:05:05.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.19,0:05:07.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:11.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！面！手！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:13.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  好迫人的氣勢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.64,0:05:15.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好！黑色！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她打垮！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明擊中了  為什麼不算數！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.98,0:05:27.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些都不是有效攻擊  小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.87,0:05:29.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要認為只要打中就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.65,0:05:32.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須準確擊中移動中的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.29,0:05:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光這一點  對外行人就很難了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.65,0:05:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還遠遠不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:41.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺川！你快還手啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  搞不好能行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:49.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出場外
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.94,0:05:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜！就差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:53.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能贏哦  小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.07,0:05:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺川你在做什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:06:01.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  怎麼樣都無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:12.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  淺川  趕快回開始線那邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.24,0:06:15.35,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我錯了\N對不起  m(>3<)m
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.38,0:06:19.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:21.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.53,0:06:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面有效
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:24.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:26.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹有效
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:28.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽結束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得不錯嘛  淺川
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:33.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind  小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.88,0:06:38.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好險啊  竟然讓我這麼擔心…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…淺川  你上哪去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.99,0:06:43.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我要回去咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.12,0:06:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我已經比完了  可以吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:50.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？還在比賽中啊！你也來給大家加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起咯  大家加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.63,0:07:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都  剛才真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:07.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要變得更強才行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.59,0:07:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會好好鍛煉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:17.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.79,0:07:40.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不被人發現偷偷離開  之後再裝作遲到進來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:44.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做些什麼好啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:52.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先我要填飽肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:59.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！面！手！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.52,0:08:00.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.22,0:08:03.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙  感覺上慌慌張張…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.56,0:08:05.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧她還這麼大塊頭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.55,0:08:03.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}室江高中·中堅  桑原鞘子（红方）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:08.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}町戶高中·中堅  西山佳戀（白方）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小西  一直逃跑會被判犯規的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大白癡！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:14.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進攻進攻！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大白癡！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.69,0:08:17.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:21.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹有效
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:27.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鞘…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.69,0:08:29.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹有效…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:34.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西山實力原本就是我們隊上最強的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被逼到絕境身體自然會做出條件性的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.36,0:08:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不被逼到絕境  反應就有點那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:44.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  這樣西山就不會輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:47.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鞘  別著急
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:51.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管給我過來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.47,0:08:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老娘看你有多難搞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:56.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.69,0:08:59.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.76,0:09:18.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鞘那傢伙  步法有這麼好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.69,0:09:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼足
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.99,0:09:40.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑擊手！打中了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.28,0:09:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太淺！力道不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.16,0:09:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出場外
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.47,0:09:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯規兩次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:56.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大白癡！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.66,0:09:58.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.06,0:10:03.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就各得一分  真是好險
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:06.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是剛才的手部算擊中就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:08.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但得分就是得分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.01,0:10:11.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面  在延長賽上取得一分就能獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鞘  加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用步法成功追上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:23.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時只是用蠻力的你  已經懂得冷靜行動了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是小珠教的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她將大家都帶動了起來  是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.46,0:10:36.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠教的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.96,0:10:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…喂喂  這不是我的工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.25,0:10:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧！小鞘！延長戰！Go！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.61,0:10:47.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.95,0:10:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:10:56.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是小鞘  我要唱了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:10:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按順序來是不是太快？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:03.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣耍詐  真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦  只是練習賽啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.12,0:11:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是練習賽  不過是練習賽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.12,0:11:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何我也不能輸！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.16,0:11:19.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  所以至少要變裝一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.85,0:11:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.93,0:11:31.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你需要的話我很樂意借給你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.18,0:11:32.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.37,0:11:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.28,0:11:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,週一要還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:38.28,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}（教導主任）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.56,0:11:58.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.79,0:12:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  到時間了  平手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜！就差一點！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.26,0:12:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鞘  你打得很好  了不起了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.53,0:12:09.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:12.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這笨蛋！怎麼淨發呆啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:18.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要好好鍛煉一下能打到延長賽的體力啊  西山
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.61,0:12:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神方面也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.34,0:12:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小珠…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.69,0:12:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:37.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武禮葉！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:40.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武禮葉！一年9班武禮葉！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:42.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好慢哦  武禮葉！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.58,0:12:43.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去換衣服吧  武禮葉！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.14,0:12:45.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武禮葉就是武禮葉！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:48.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:51.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.75,0:12:53.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要小珠再出場大將戰？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.66,0:12:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是擔任先鋒的那個女孩子吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.35,0:13:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  我也想再看一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:03.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和我打的那個女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.89,0:13:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是先鋒女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是剛才的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.34,0:13:10.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  原田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.01,0:13:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不希望只有自己沒有對手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:14.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:17.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想和她較量一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.39,0:13:19.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下子可有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.17,0:13:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠你咯！紀梨乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.95,0:13:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為部長要給我贏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.98,0:13:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎  你要努力當計時員哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.55,0:13:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.35,0:13:32.84,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}室江高中·副將  千葉紀梨乃（紅方）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:35.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}町戶高中·副將  安藤優梨（白方）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:29.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副將
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅方  千葉紀梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.43,0:13:35.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白方  安藤優梨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.39,0:13:37.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.24,0:13:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  我完全沒有去加油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真對不起大家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.62,0:14:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃  別被壓下去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.72,0:14:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按B連打！連打！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好討厭…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.81,0:14:20.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她故意的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.42,0:14:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是惡意騷擾吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:24.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是惡意騷擾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.37,0:14:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安藤她想贏吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.75,0:14:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起獲勝她更想欺負人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是纏鬥卻不主動進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.39,0:14:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真難對付呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我當她對手就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:43.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都你變成黑色  變成黑色了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.04,0:14:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力用力！安藤！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.52,0:14:46.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揍飛她！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:54.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.27,0:14:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安藤你…差點就犯規了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.26,0:15:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要緊吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:07.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題  紀梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.53,0:15:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想靠那種不正經手段取勝的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.41,0:15:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是贏不了你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:15.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牢記小珠的指導放手一戰吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的指導呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.99,0:15:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像平日一樣穩紮穩打
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:25.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以你自身那率真的劍道  定能取勝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.37,0:15:26.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:27.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在對方進攻之前  使用腕力讓竹劍像畫半圓一樣把對方的竹劍彈開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後  在揮下自己竹劍的方向上施加力量就成了攻擊動作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手——！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是太狡猾了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.93,0:16:05.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是很喜歡動畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.12,0:16:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是這次的練習賽贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:10.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就把我珍藏的的超夢幻逸品送你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超夢幻逸品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.71,0:16:18.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃！上啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:20.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡  進攻！打她！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿下！紀梨乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  小珠也來一起加油嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要大聲！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加…加油…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.53,0:16:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.53,0:16:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要大聲…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.05,0:16:39.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎  好時機
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.34,0:16:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！面！面！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加…加油…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.51,0:16:54.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣聽不到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.05,0:17:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是面？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.48,0:17:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目標其實是腹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.04,0:17:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就直接用碰體來撞飛你！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.93,0:17:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:16.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面有效！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.92,0:17:18.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:19.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽結束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.16,0:17:21.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少給我拿一分啊！大白癡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好  紀梨乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是部長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.41,0:17:29.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…前輩…恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.58,0:17:32.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝小珠你幫我加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我贏了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:41.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面有效…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩勝一負一平手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.47,0:17:51.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照我所教的去做的話一定會獲勝的！珠姬！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼都沒教她啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.52,0:17:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點戴上頭盔吧  小…武禮葉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.40,0:17:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.33,0:18:02.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橫尾  你也快去準備啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.15,0:18:04.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:07.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想安心地看比賽啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像蠻強的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.78,0:18:30.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明那麼小一隻卻總覺得很強
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.72,0:18:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  實際上也很強
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.65,0:18:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  不快點戴上頭盔的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:38.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原田
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:40.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得我能贏她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.73,0:18:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.62,0:18:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～好久沒有這樣的感覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:55.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先拿一分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.58,0:18:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:18:59.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大將  上前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.92,0:19:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  怎麼了武禮葉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:05.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又忘記名布了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.75,0:19:07.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法呀  武禮葉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.47,0:19:09.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你神經還真是大條啊  武禮葉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.57,0:19:17.76,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}室江高中·大將  武禮葉（紅方）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:20.72,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}町戶高中·大將  橫尾摩耶（白方）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.07,0:19:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大將戰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅方  武…武禮葉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.43,0:19:20.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白方  橫尾摩耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.23,0:19:26.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體型差太多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.65,0:19:29.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太狡猾了！你太大塊了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:32.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣子小珠不會被撞飛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:33.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來會有一場精彩的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.78,0:19:36.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該會打延長戰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:37.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.39,0:19:47.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.07,0:19:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面——！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.73,0:20:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面有效
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.21,0:20:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:08.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二局
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:11.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.20,0:20:14.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等下啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.55,0:20:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面——！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.99,0:20:33.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面有效
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.24,0:20:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.61,0:20:38.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武禮葉！武禮葉！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:40.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽結束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.37,0:20:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都…什麼都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.18,0:20:55.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去敬禮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.93,0:20:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三勝一敗一和  室江高中獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.31,0:21:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩隊互相  敬禮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.97,0:21:03.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝指教
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.43,0:21:07.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.67,0:21:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太太太太太————太好啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.16,0:21:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩  真是一場好比賽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.99,0:21:25.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是前輩的學生  大家都很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.48,0:21:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好  武禮葉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.84,0:21:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起呀  武禮葉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.83,0:21:32.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.22,0:21:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小次郎  能不能讓我也來比一場
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.07,0:21:40.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  但剛才你說我們再比也沒什麼意義…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.50,0:21:43.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算啦  我是無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.23,0:21:45.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去拿護具…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.36,0:21:46.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒在說你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.93,0:21:54.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.52,0:21:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  武…武禮…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:21:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.67,0:22:07.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室江高中一年級  川添珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.95,0:22:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是石橋賢三郎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.71,0:22:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添珠姬  與我一決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.64,0:23:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}　BAMBL{\r}\NBAMBOO BLADE  簡稱「バンブレ」  已經要到第七話了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.35,0:23:56.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為慶祝  我來表演單字作文
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.38,0:24:00.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…請一直用到最後的「レ」以各字為句首即興連成一段話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.21,0:24:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好  瞭解了  這個我可是很拿手的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.75,0:24:04.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.27,0:24:06.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「バ」  啪的一聲擊中面部
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.01,0:24:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「ン」  嗯  卻被裁判說太輕了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.23,0:24:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「ブ」  嘀嘀咕咕只怪裁判不公平
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.93,0:24:15.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「レ」  啊…遺憾  沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.06,0:24:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此  下集是「壽司與炸肉餅」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.99,0:24:20.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣應該可以了吧
